A repo for experiments with deploying to AWS.

Set Up

1) git submodule update --recursive (gets all included submodules) 

2) Copy lib/aws-sdk/config-sample.inc.php to lib/aws-sdk/config.inc.php as described at http://aws.amazon.com/articles/PHP/4261

Repo Contents

 - bin/simple-deploy

Some simple scripts that initialise AWS features individually. EC2, CloudFront, S3.
These will form part of the more complex deployment tasks at a later date. 